      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 2 Travel Advisory item about new Ritz-Carlton Hotel in Philadelphia, which misstated its distance from Independence Hall and misstated nature of renovation work (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the Travel Advisory column on July 2 about the new Ritz-Carlton Hotel in Philadelphia misstated its distance from Independence Hall. It is not near Independence Hall but rather eight blocks away. A caption with the report misstated the nature of work on the hotel. It was under renovation, not under construction.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
